{"tid":270783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎智英爆粗怒屌「東方日報」記者","createTime":"2017-06-04T14:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T18:55:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44267142915a758500d64f3d9a6a9f5597e02245","tid":270783,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/221507_6ec2a524698907ddc3b7bdeee59239f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F221507_6ec2a524698907ddc3b7bdeee59239f0.jpg&h=01b5f6ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎智英大鑊了！本身是天主教徒、經常將民主自由掛在口邊的壹傳媒黎智英，今晚到維園出席支聯會舉辦的六四燭光悼念集會時，公然用「X你老母X」的粗口，指罵在場進行正常採訪工作的東網記者，威脅新聞自由。期間黎智英更稱「我實搞你」、「我影X咗你相㗎」，有刑事恐嚇之嫌。 <br />\n今日傍晚約6時半，外號「漢奸黎」的黎智英，與外號「李漢奸」、同屬天主教徒的民主黨創黨主席李柱銘，一同來到銅鑼灣維多利亞公園。兩人首先來到維園涼亭，出席由天主教正義和平委員會舉行的六四祈禱會。其中黎智英彎身準備坐在地上時，一時失平衡差點跌個四腳朝天，幸最後沒有受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n到7時許祈禱會將近完結時，黎智英與李柱銘站起身準備離開，多名記者立即一湧而上要求訪問兩人。黎智英應酬了記者兩句後，突然急步走向一名東網男記者面前，一邊用右手指着記者，一邊以粗口辱罵記者近距離拍攝他：「我實搞你，我依家話畀你聽，我影X咗你張相㗎！...X你老母X！」 <br />\n<br />\n期間東網記者一直面帶微笑、禮貌地應對黎智英的辱罵，並澄清自己沒有近距離拍攝他。黎智英發洩完一輪後，便與李柱銘一同步往位於維園硬地足球場的燭光集會會場，與家人會合一同悼念六四。"},{"pid":"3d19d0b4a822c0f35ce4c71a913e71e4e1eb0e82","tid":270783,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:15:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170604/mobile/bkn-20170604203028576-0604_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170604%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170604203028576-0604_00822_001.html&d=DKvAiAsYFaNpUWw8J7SPi54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=52a6fd6d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170604/mobile/bkn-20170604203028576-0604_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bba9727f97a7fc84325dcd3a640579a4714e6439","tid":270783,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a52514ee982f739b91b89644a753e77f7a65dab","tid":270783,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d179f6210895831bd10db9c45dafe66a2adacf8c","tid":270783,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:22:56.000Z","msg":"基哥.jpg"},{"pid":"418c17abf1339b4034621e02d897e84186dcbc64","tid":270783,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea8368b188ce840140d3f5ba3003108a235e386","tid":270783,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef8f04f8414cda0ddef8c252f031e0828bf0fc2","tid":270783,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"咁都叫新聞真係好撚好笑"},{"pid":"19758e76f5fe999c4d01cd644321963260261b08","tid":270783,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:46:24.000Z","msg":"跟據香港公安，佢邊有講粗口？"},{"pid":"5f4bee8450e698b5db13e78747a09514d9d67246","tid":270783,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都叫新聞真係好撚好笑</blockquote><br />\n馬英九看手錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a442203ad672d11a9cc0309d969117ed35b305","tid":270783,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea30af7557a472bc41df38f3b4bf9a268ea7817c","tid":270783,"uid":84633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi